none.description:
{Misfortune}

Decreases Luck of target enemy unit by -1.

While Misfortune lasts, Luck bonuses cannot raise that unit above -1 Luck.

basic.description:
{Basic Misfortune}

Decreases Luck of target enemy unit by -1.

While Misfortune lasts, Luck bonuses cannot raise that unit above -1 Luck.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Misfortune}

Decreases Luck of target enemy unit by -2.

While Misfortune lasts, Luck bonuses cannot raise that unit above -2 Luck.

expert.description:
{Expert Misfortune}

Decreases Luck of all enemy units by -2.

While Misfortune lasts, Luck bonuses cannot raise affected units above -2 Luck.
